The paper deals with text mining and data analysis, which are common topics in the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories. The focus on software engineering and replicability suggests that the Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-category is also relevant. The use of clustering and stability metrics suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-categories.
